  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Kdenlive</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Kdenlive</application> package is a KF6 based video
      editor.
    </para>

    &lfs123_checked;

    <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Package Information</bridgehead>
